thread.title: Ollie Blake
thread.title_full: Lauryn Rose reviewed by Ollie Blake

author: Ollie Blake
title: Ollie Blake
text:
I ordered a necklace with gold leaf design as a mothers day present.
It was delivered the next day. The necklace is beautiful and was very much appreciated.
I was delighted that 10% of the cost goes to LauraLynn house.
Overall, beautiful product and very quick delivery, would definitely recommend a a gift option for any occasion.
